name: IA Clarington Loomis Global Equity Opportunities Fund
longDescription: To achieve the investment objective, The Fund's strategy is to invest primarily in a diversified portfolio of equity securities of companies located anywhere in the world. The Funds objective is to provide longterm capital appreciation.
